https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/k3v2MSF1rFgiXrIlSUlDlMhlq6q.jpg Sharp-tongued and outspoken, comedian and star of the FX firefighter comedy-drama "Rescue Me" Denis Leary brings his acerbic wit to New York's Town Hall, joined by fellow stand-up talents Lenny Clarke, Whitney Cummings and Adam Ferrara.
